{"id":"304707944_La_ville_fonctionnelle_et_les_modeles_urbains_qui_lui_ont_succede_Exemples_d'une_pratique_politique_en_train_de_se_globaliser","abstract":"Dans le discours public et les pratiques de la gestion urbaine, plusieurs modeles apportent des reponses a la question de savoir comment faire evoluer la/notre ville. Cet article presente une typologie d’une douzaine de ces modeles selon leur portee et leur approche du phenomene urbain. L’origine et la diffusion des modeles sont decrits depuis la ville fonctionnelle de Le Corbusier/CIAM.","authors":["Herman van der Wusten"],"meta":["June 2016EchoGéo 36(36)","DOI:10.4000/echogeo.14634"],"references":["289652074_New_Public_Management_and_Governance_A_Comparison","251059589_Democratie_participative_et_gouvernance_interactive_au_Bresil_Santos_Porto_Alegre_et_Curitiba","298103117_The_contribution_of_university-industry-government_interactions_to_creative_entrepreneurship_and_economic_development","289641766_Governance_Networks","287234225_World_City_Network_A_Global_Urban_Analysis","274529291_World_Politics_by_Other_Means_London_City_Diplomacy_and_the_Olympics","254797994_Het_Algemeen_Uitbreidingsplan_van_Amsterdam","247822555_The_Creative_Economy_How_People_Make_Money_from_Ideas","240491158_Defensible_Space_Crime_Prevention_Through_Urban_Design","238337354_The_Creative_City-A_Toolkit_for_Urban_Innovators","215613841_Development_Good_Governance_and_Local_Democracy","229397707_Mobilizing_Policy_Models_Methods_and_Mutations","228007576_The_World_City_Hypothesis","36731246_The_keys_to_success_the_social_sporting_economic_and_communications_impact_of_Barcelona'92","24103751_Growth_in_Cities"]}